{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "金梅龄在昏迷中醒来，发现长江水寇赵老大和老王企图对她不轨。她虽然身体虚弱，但仍出手击毙了赵老大。随后，长江水路副总瓢把子孙超远赶到，认出金梅龄是“毒君”金一鹏的女儿，对其极为恭敬，并杀死了老王。孙超远将金梅龄带回船上，会见了长江水路总瓢把子小龙神贺信雄。金梅龄请求贺信雄送她去武汉。到达武汉后，金梅龄得知辛捷失踪的消息，并前往山梅珠宝号打听情况。在珠宝号，她遇到了一位神秘的瘦削老人，老人对她姓金且是金一鹏之女的事实反应异常。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "老王，你可不能不讲交情，这小妞儿是我发现的，至少得让我占个头筹，你乱动什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "text": "你怎么恁地小气，摸一把有什么关系？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "不准你摸。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "text": "好好，不摸就是不摸。喂，你也得快一点呀，等先完事了，我还想辄进一腿呢，不然等会孙老二来了，大家都没份。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个不长眼睛的杀胚，你是找死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "也没看见你这样性急的人，这小妞还没有醒，弄起来没有味道。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "好好，依你，我就马马虎虎先弄一下吧！可是咱们得先讲好了，这小妞是我的，你要插一脚也可以，可得先拿点银子来孝敬孝敬我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "text": "赵老大的话，还有什么问题，这小妞比首善里的窑姐儿好多了，一两银子一次都值。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "老王，你站远点。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "text": "好，我站远点就站远点。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "站住。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "金姑娘好……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "在下不知道金姑娘大驾光临，有失远迎，务请移玉敝舟，容在下略表寸心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "这厮是你的手下吗？我看早该将他……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "text": "好教大哥得知，今日小弟却请来一位贵宾呢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "text": "这位姑娘就是金欹金大侠的师妹，'北君'的掌珠，金姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "小龙神贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "今天是哪阵风把姑娘吹来的，快坐快坐。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "小龙神贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "这位姑娘倒豪爽得紧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "金姑娘要到什么地方去，可要我弟兄送一程？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天地虽大，但何处是我的容身之所呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "小龙神贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "姑娘心里有什么事，只管告诉兄弟好了，兄弟虽然无用，大小也还能帮姑娘个忙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "text": "我正有事要找贺大哥帮忙。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "小龙神贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "姑娘有事只管说，我小龙神贺信雄，不是在姑娘面前夸口，南七省地面上大大小小的事，都还能提得起来。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_long_shen_he_xin_xiong",
      "text": "那么就请贺大哥送我到武汉去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xin_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "小龙神贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "这个太容易了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_he_xin_xiong",
      "text": "然后还请二位替我准备一只船，以及几个水手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_he_xin_xiong",
      "text": "我想出海，所以二位必须要替我找几个熟悉水性的船夫。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xin_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "小龙神贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "这个也容易，我手下有许多人，原本就是在沿海讨生活的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "既然姑娘要到武汉去，必定有着急事，那么我们也不必再在此停泊了，今夜连夜就开始吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "这样再好没有了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "姑娘有事，就请到岸上去办，至迟今夜明晨，我等就可以将姑娘要的船和水手准备好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "姑娘，快走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "等会再说。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_gong_shen_dan_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "孙二哥，这事就拜托你了，千万不要忘记。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_jin_gong_shen_dan_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "这件事包在我身上，不过范大哥却再也别把这事算在我账上了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "孙二哥，你来得正好。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "怎地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "这两天汉口又出了许多事，第一件便是此间新起的巨商，山梅珠宝号的东主辛捷，居然失踪，人言纷纷，都说他一定是给绑票了……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "这又算得了什么大事？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "孙二哥你不知道，这个辛捷，却不是个普通商人呢！他不但和小弟有些交情，便是和'崆峒三绝剑'的地绝剑于一飞也是好友，岂有人绑了此人的票，只怕有些不妥。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "范大哥莫非疑心是我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "我倒无所谓，那于一飞昨天突然又折回汉口……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "那于一飞不是日前就回转崆峒山了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "本来，我也听到他说要立刻回崆峒，将他在此间和武当派所生的纠葛，以及七妙神君的突然出现，回山去告诉剑神厉大侠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "哦，这一下'崆峒三绝剑'居然全到了鄂中，我们又有热闹好看了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "这位地绝剑一到此间，便听到山梅珠宝号店东辛捷失踪的消息，生气的不得了，找着小弟说，这事一定又是长江水路上的人干出来的事情，想乘机索金银……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "范大哥怎地说这般话，须知小弟虽是强盗，但盗亦有道，我们也有我们的规矩，吃我们水路上饭的人，就是陆地上放着成堆的金银财宝，我们也不会望一眼。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "我也是这么说，而且孙二哥，你不知道，据我看这位辛老板的失踪，其中还关系着另外一个人呢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "就是这位主儿的师父。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "这倒真的奇怪了，想那姓辛的一个商人，怎会与他老人家生出关系来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "可是于一飞却一定要说是小龙神贺大哥和你孙二哥手下的人干出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "今天清晨，于一飞便和他的师兄、师妹，北上武当山了，临行时，他还再来嘱咐小弟，一定要找出那位姓辛的下落，不过老实说，姓辛的失踪，也真有点奇怪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "金弓神弹范治成",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "而且他这人根本就是怪人，只是我却想不透，毒君金一鹏若是想对付他，又何必要邀他到船上去，何况毒君根本就没有要对付他的理由呀！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "孙超远",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘要到山梅珠宝号去，你可识得路吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "车夫",
      "listener": "char_sun_chao_yuan",
      "text": "认得，认得，你家只管放心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快点走，快点走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "车夫",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "这两天山梅号的辛老板教土匪给绑了票，连店门都关起来啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "姑娘找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "speaker_name": "金梅龄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我找你们这里的管事的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_jin_mei_ling",
      "text": "请你家等一会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 432,
